{
  "stem": "17845.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And she decided to take lessons, private lessons.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So-- so I actually never went to first class.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I went right away to the second class.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he-- they-- they-- they had a stand where they were selling newspapers.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And just before the war, I think '38, Mom was tell me-- I can't remember exactly.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They took away their rights for them to sell.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So my father went and intervened.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they were able-- otherwise they would have starved.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They wouldn't have had no more to live.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So that's one of the examples what he did.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But he did a lot of good, he really was his--",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I still remember, in fact, when there's a Polish national holiday, like the 3rd of May.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Right?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So the Jewish children used to go to the synagogue.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the Christians used to go to the church.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And there used to be celebrations and speeches.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And my father always, he was on the [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He would stand up, and I was so proud of him that he talks to the whole school.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "That's my father.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was something, because looking always towards it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Was that in the-- in the [?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Yavna ?] school?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was-- No, no.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That was from the-- from the public school.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He was chosen to speak.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He was a very good speaker.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And so I was very proud of him.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because he did a lot of things for us during the war.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Because of him, we really survived this.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He helped us in every way, always with a smile and a joke.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he was a wonderful fellow.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "At home we spoke Polish and Yiddish.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Mostly Polish, mostly Polish with my friends I spoke.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "At school, Polish.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Polish, Yiddish too, but my Yiddish was atrocious.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
